headline: Better Dividend Stock: JPMorgan Chase vs. Goldman Sachs
summary: Despite these uncertainties, reliable and high-quality dividend income from a diversified portfolio can be a great option for investors to ride out stock market turbulence.  Let's discuss which of these financial titans is the better dividend stock to buy now.  In this case, it's not a coincidence that shares of JPMorgan have outperformed the broader market, returning 30% over the past year.
